data.description: Welcome to Brookside! Built in 2015, the home is situated on a generous 1-acre lot with great mountain views, including a direct view of Pikes Peak. The split bedroom design offers comfort and privacy for everyone in the household. Upon stepping inside you will be greeted by the warm ambiance of the generous living space. The well-appointed kitchen is complete with modern appliances and ample counter space. The large lot provides ample space for outdoor activities and offers the convenience of RV parking. 4 Bedrooms, 2 bonus rooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, with an oversized 3 car attached garage may be just right for  you! One of the standout features of this property is the three-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles, storage, or a workshop. Whether you have a passion for cars or simply need extra space, this garage will exceed your expectations. Schedule your tour today!
